        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 6 at 2:29PM MDT until June 6 at 3:00PM MDT by NWS Grand Junction CO</headline>
        <description>SVRGJT

The National Weather Service in Grand Junction has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northwestern Mesa County in west central Colorado...
Southwestern Garfield County in west central Colorado...

* Until 300 PM MDT.

* At 229 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 17 miles northwest
of Fruita moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
northwestern Mesa and southwestern Garfield Counties.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
